\end_layout

\end_inset

a list of 
\begin_inset Formula $M$
\end_inset

 pollutants 
\begin_inset Formula $m=1,...,M$
\end_inset

 are evaluated. Treatment target 
\begin_inset Formula $\tau_j^m$
\end_inset

 is set for each pollutant 
\begin_inset Formula $m$
\end_inset

 and each potential site 
\begin_inset Formula $j$
\end_inset

. 
\end_layout

